snippet.title: NAIRI: Tower of Shirin - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
In NAIRI:Tower of Shirin, you can...

✔️Enjoy hand drawn cute graphics!
✔️Meet adorable characters and animals!
✔️Solve engaging puzzles!
✔️Experience atmospheric music!
